  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Sales Executive (Coffee Machines &amp; Beans)</p>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> [Insert City/Region]</p>\n<p><strong>About Us:</strong><br>\nWe are a growing company in the coffee solutions industry, supplying high-quality coffee machines and beans to offices, cafés, and F&amp;B establishments. We provide excellent service, fresh coffee, and tailored solutions that make businesses run better.</p>\n<p><strong>Role Overview:</strong><br>\nThe <strong>main goal</strong> of this role is to <strong>sell coffee beans and machines</strong> by proactively reaching out to new prospects and nurturing long-term customer relationships. You will be the face of our company, introducing our products to businesses through cold calls, walk-ins, and showroom visits.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Sell coffee beans and coffee machines directly to businesses.</li>\n  <li>Proactively engage in <strong>cold calling</strong> and <strong>cold walking</strong> into offices, shops, and F&amp;B outlets.</li>\n  <li>Distribute samples, explain product benefits clearly, and secure follow-up meetings.</li>\n  <li>Invite prospects to our <strong>coffee machine showroom</strong> for demonstrations.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a strong sales pipeline and achieve monthly sales targets.</li>\n  <li>Follow up consistently with customers to close deals and build relationships.</li>\n  <li>Provide <strong>daily updates</strong> and reports to your superior on activities and results.</li>\n  <li>Manage your schedule, appointments, and customer follow-ups independently.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven sales experience (F&amp;B, office solutions, or related B2B preferred).</li>\n  <li>Confident in <strong>cold calling</strong> and <strong>face-to-face sales</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication, presentation, and persuasion skills.</li>\n  <li>Highly motivated, disciplined, and able to manage your time well.</li>\n  <li>Must be experienced in customer follow-up and relationship management.</li>\n  <li><strong>Bonus:</strong> Possess a valid car driving license (for easier client visits).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Basic salary + attractive commission &amp; performance incentives.</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for career progression in a fast-growing company.</li>\n  <li>A supportive team culture with a love for great coffee.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Main Goal of the Role:</strong><br>\nTo <strong>sell coffee beans and machines</strong> by reaching new prospects, passing samples, explaining products clearly, following up diligently, and bringing potential customers to our showroom for demonstrations.</p>",
